=========== preparation ===========

In custom_openstack_client.py set next variables

  ADMIN_USER_ID
  ADMIN_USER_PASSWORD
  ADMIN_PROJECT_ID

In main.py set next variables

  KEYSTONE_PUBLIC_URL
  GLANCE_PUBLIC_URL
  NEUTRON_PUBLIC_URL
  HORIZON_BASE_URL

User ID can be fetch by using 'keystone user-list' command
Project ID can be fetch by using 'keystone tenant-list' command
Service URLs can be fetch by using 'keystone endpoint-list' command

!!! DO NOT FORGET TO UPDATE QUOTAS !!!
Check Admin -> System -> Default page in Horizon and set quotas to make possible
create needed number of volumes, snapshots and so on.

!!! DO NOT FORGET TO NUMBER OF ITEMS PER PAGE !!!
Got to Admin -> Settings -> User Settings -> Items Per Page and set needed value.

============ execution ============

cd horizon_load_test
virtualenv .
source bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m unittest -v main.HorizonLoadTest